Class ManagerController

java.lang.Object
controller.ManagerController
All Implemented Interfaces:
IManagerServices
public class ManagerController extends Object implements IManagerServices
Provides all management operations for the Manager role:
  • Create, edit, delete BTO projects
  • View all projects or only own projects
  • Toggle project visibility
  • Handle officer registrations
  • Process applicant applications and withdrawals
  • Generate summary reports
  • View and reply to enquiries
Since:
24/4/2025
Version:

Author:
